message: Namaste. Aap kaafi pareshaan lag rahe ho. Bataiye, kya chal raha hai?
Mera recent breakup hua hai. Samajh nahi aa raha move on kaise karun.
Main aapki kundli dekh rahi hoon. Yeh separation temporary phase lag raha hai, aap emotionally strong ho.
Kya future mein patch up ya naya relationship possible hai?
Ji haan. Agle 3 mahino mein positive change dikh raha hai.
AstroTalk par aap detail mein personal guidance le sakte ho, pehla chat bilkul FREE hota hai.
Theek hai, main AstroTalk par hi baat continue karta hoon. Thank you.
